{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/blocks_english.png?t=1733752597\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/GIF_Steam_01.gif?t=1733752597\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Creativity meets production in Block Factory, an automation game with a clear purpose: building sets of captivating 3D figurines. Design and optimize your factory to efficiently produce and assemble toy blocks into finished figurines. Analyze blueprints and meticulously plan your assembly lines, orchestrating the production of blocks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build specialized machines that streamline the gathering and transformation process, shaping blocks into charming figurines. Create intricate assembly lines to stack, glue, and assemble hundreds of blocks, bringing your models to life! Optimize and enhance every step of the journey to ensure your enchanting figurines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/lignebf7.gif?t=1733752597\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/automate_english.png?t=1733752597\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/GIF_Steam_02.gif?t=1733752597\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Encounter and overcome automation and logistic challenges as you explore the vast landscape of complex mechanics within your factory. From cutting and shaping to stacking, painting and mixing colors, automate every aspect of the shape-processing journey. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new technologies and expand your factory's capabilities. Learn, improve, rebuild, and conquer logistical challenges to design the most efficient production lines imaginable. Welcome to a realm where innovation meets automation, and your creative prowess knows no bounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/lignebf7.gif?t=1733752597\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/dioramas_english.png?t=1733752597\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/GIF_Steam_03.gif?t=1733752597\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Assemble figurines from your production lines. Your constructions find their place in dioramas, serving as rewards for your skill. As your assembly line evolves, so do the enchanting scenes within the dioramas. Witness the result unfold, figure by figure, diorama by diorama.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/lignebf7.gif?t=1733752597\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/share_english.png?t=1733752597\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/GIF_Steam_01_3.gif?t=1733752597\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Creative mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create, share, and build your own figurines and dioramas on the Steam Workshop! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733752597","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/page.bg.jpg?t=1733752597","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733752597","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733752597","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3209880,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>Join our Discord!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/blocks_english.png?t=1733752597\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/GIF_Steam_01.gif?t=1733752597\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Creativity meets production in Block Factory, an automation game with a clear purpose: building sets of captivating 3D figurines. Design and optimize your factory to efficiently produce and assemble toy blocks into finished figurines. Analyze blueprints and meticulously plan your assembly lines, orchestrating the production of blocks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build specialized machines that streamline the gathering and transformation process, shaping blocks into charming figurines. Create intricate assembly lines to stack, glue, and assemble hundreds of blocks, bringing your models to life! Optimize and enhance every step of the journey to ensure your enchanting figurines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827680/extras/lignebf7.gif?t=1733752597\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste